latestIgtvVideos.title: Mnt Premium
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Here i am reviewing on an amazing products of @mntpremium

I received two products -
👉🏻 Aloe vera multipurpose gel for skin and hair with cucumber and vitamins
👉🏻 Tea tree night gel mask with cucumber and green tea extract

🔴 No paraben mineral oil and silicon
🔴 Unisex
🔴 All skin types

It is also available on Amazon👍🏻

⭕⭕DESCRIPTION⭕⭕

GEL - Pure and organic aloe vera gel. It can be use for both hair and skin. Ideal for oily skin, and it can help treat dry skin too

MASK - It helps to brighten and remove the dark spots. It helps combat  black heads, sun damage , dark spots, purify , detoxify skin

⭕⭕HOW TO USE⭕⭕

GEL - Apply gently on skin or hair and leave on for 30 mins, after that rinse with water.

MASK -Clean your face with a mild face wash. Apply a generous layer of night gel mask on face and neck. Gently massage in circular motion with your fingertips. Let the calmness of the gel sink in your skin. Use before bed time to get fresh glowing skin every morning.

Thankyou for sending me this amazing product @mntpremium
